item.title: Prayer bpn6315 in Namibia
item.description: #NGURANGURA ##(MORNING) Nina pinduka mouvando Woge, Ove Karunga gwange, ano yamuwapera ogu a papara uvando, a kare monzugo zoge zoKupongoka megameno Lyoge nouvando welipopero Lyoge. Twedera monda zange, Hompa gwange, nosite sokupuma-kwezuva sehoramo, ngwendi moomu ono twedere nge site songurangura soufenkenda Woge. (Source category: Rukwangali: NGURANGURA) (Bahaiprayers.net ID: 6315)

item.title: Prayer bpn6316 in Namibia
item.description: Ame kuna pinduka mongurangura ozi monkenda Zoge, Karunga gwange, nina tundu monzugo zange nehuguvaro moge, yiyo nina ligava nyamwange ketakameso Lyoge. Hegumuna nkenda Zoge, makandayiko gokoruha Roge pwange, ntani ninka ni tare nzugo ngwendi moomu ono ninkinge ni rupuke mepopero Lyoge ano magano gange gandjikiti Pwoge. Kutupu ko Karunga gokupita Pwoge, Ove Ohuru, Mudilikufanekesa, Mudivi-nayinye, Musikiliromo. (Source category: Rukwangali: NGURANGURA) (Bahaiprayers.net ID: 6316)
